to compile, run make under respective directories
for sumac, can build library using make lib
note: the Makefile's are edited
make sure 32 and 64 compilation are specified
flags in sumac/vite:
vite: -DUSE_32_BIT_GRAPH
sumac: -DUSE_32BIT_GRAPH

to run the executable, convert the mtx files to bin format using vite library:
./vite/bin/fileConvert -m -f debug-mat.mtx -o debug-mat.mtx.bin

run the sumac code
./sumac/LDgpu/ldgpu1 debug-mat.mtx.bin 1
the 2nd parameter is number of batches (in case the graph is big)
